column3: Can you please quantify the speedup, for example with benchmark results?

@laanwj thank you for your comment.

When measuring with the ```bench_bitcoin``` command on my iMac(macOS 10.13.2, i5 2.9GHz, mem 8G, HDD), the following result was reported.

CCheckQueueSpeedPrevectorJob => 9% faster
PrevectorClear => 38% faster
PrevectorDestructor => 47% faster

[command line that actually using]
